@startuml sequence-poi-priority-conflict
title POI Priority Conflict — Winner-Only Narration
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

actor       "Du khách"     as U
participant "MapPage"      as Map
participant "NarrationMgr" as Nar
participant "Audio/TTS"    as Audio

note over U : Đứng giữa vùng chồng lấn\n[POI-A level=2, POI-B level=1]

U -> Map : GeofenceEvent(POI-A, ENTER)
U -> Map : GeofenceEvent(POI-B, ENTER)

Map -> Nar : HandleAsync(POI-A, level=2)
note right of Nar : Queue rỗng → thêm POI-A
Nar -> Audio : Play POI-A 🔊

Map -> Nar : HandleAsync(POI-B, level=1)
note right of Nar
  Kiểm tra queue:
  POI-A (level=2) > POI-B (level=1)
  → **Loại bỏ POI-B** ✗
end note
Nar --> Map : (return — discarded)

Audio --> U : 🔊 Nghe POI-A
@enduml
